  "3135030": {
    "name": "Deep Tactics - Journey of the Wizard",
    "steam_appid": 3135030,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/429ba27160e0e6ff6a0bb72392510e71.avif?t=1768206492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras_big/429ba27160e0e6ff6a0bb72392510e71.avif?t=1768206492 width=800 height=391 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/cd66ff0c1b1bee95f1fdb7501273ab59.avif?t=1768206492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras_big/cd66ff0c1b1bee95f1fdb7501273ab59.avif?t=1768206492 width=800 height=67 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience this colourful, varied reinterpretation of well-known strategy game classics such as ‘Advance Wars’ or ‘Nectaris’ in a fresh, fantastic new look on your PC. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move &amp; Attack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move your troops across the playing field turn by turn. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each turn, one unit can move and/or attack an opponent.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Move &amp; Attack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move your troops across the playing field in turns. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One unit can move and/or attack an opponent per turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/1707138119b1b12e7e5670411caad63b.poster.avif?t=1768206492\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/1707138119b1b12e7e5670411caad63b.webm?t=1768206492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/1707138119b1b12e7e5670411caad63b.mp4?t=1768206492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/cd66ff0c1b1bee95f1fdb7501273ab59.avif?t=1768206492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras_big/cd66ff0c1b1bee95f1fdb7501273ab59.avif?t=1768206492 width=800 height=67 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A wide variety of units</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are different units with different strengths and weaknesses. For example, a catapult is extremely strong against units inside fortifications. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, a catapult is not particularly mobile. During a turn, it can only move OR attack, which requires appropriate advance planning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/392d44fe57060035720dd488cd0faaf8.poster.avif?t=1768206492\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/392d44fe57060035720dd488cd0faaf8.webm?t=1768206492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/392d44fe57060035720dd488cd0faaf8.mp4?t=1768206492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Priests, on the other hand, are weakly armoured and completely helpless in battle, but can heal other units and, more importantly, teleport foot troops over long distances!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/a11c7a974b6aba714c3f06ba4d432ea1.poster.avif?t=1768206492\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/a11c7a974b6aba714c3f06ba4d432ea1.webm?t=1768206492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/a11c7a974b6aba714c3f06ba4d432ea1.mp4?t=1768206492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/cd66ff0c1b1bee95f1fdb7501273ab59.avif?t=1768206492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras_big/cd66ff0c1b1bee95f1fdb7501273ab59.avif?t=1768206492 width=800 height=67 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your units gain experience through battles, represented by a growing star. The more experienced a unit is, the more powerful it becomes in battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/1d022b651ed01fc47487cb8c1e8464bc.poster.avif?t=1768206492\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/1d022b651ed01fc47487cb8c1e8464bc.webm?t=1768206492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/1d022b651ed01fc47487cb8c1e8464bc.mp4?t=1768206492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/cd66ff0c1b1bee95f1fdb7501273ab59.avif?t=1768206492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras_big/cd66ff0c1b1bee95f1fdb7501273ab59.avif?t=1768206492 width=800 height=67 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And heroes, of course!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your hero enters the playing field via the <strong>main fortress</strong>. Heroes can either <strong>fight</strong> and <strong>conquer</strong> villages, <strong>search</strong> for treasures, <strong>hunt</strong> monsters or <strong>occupy</strong> magical rune fields. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When conquered, these runes trigger permanent <strong>boosts </strong>for your army. These last until another hero can conquer them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heroes also provide many tactical options. For example, special <strong>hero units</strong> can be acquired in the main fortress or powerful <strong>special actions</strong> can be triggered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/f20cd889276e5201de62822c223e7498.poster.avif?t=1768206492\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/f20cd889276e5201de62822c223e7498.webm?t=1768206492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135030/extras/f20cd889276e5201de62822c223e7498.mp4?t=1768206492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strong and dynamic AI</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of unlockable battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Varied campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different heroes with their own special units and special actions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable map generator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many tactical features such as ‘magic runes’, ‘experience’, ‘flank protection’, etc.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepad support</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Details</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat your opponent on a playing field organised into hexes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The playing field contains various terrains such as forests, mountains and lakes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Furthermore, there are towns, castles, harbours, strongholds, fortresses and more. These towns must be conquered and held by foot troops. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This allows you to increase your gold income and recruit many different units. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The heroes play a special role. They enter the playing field via your main fortress and can take part in the battle. They can also collect treasure chests, conquer powerful rune fields or fight creatures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have collected enough souls through battles, heroes can perform a particularly powerful special action to turn the battle in your favour. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only with tactical skill and foresight can you defeat the computer opponent or other players. </p>",
